### Seaman's Rules
* Rule #12 - **Failure** is a perquisite to success
    * if you will not fail then you will never succeed
    * the pain of failure is washed away by success
    * learn how not to do things
    * experience is the lessons we learn
  
---

### Incremental Development
* Select one feature
* Limit each loop to 20 minutes of time
* Build code and test pages

### Development Workflow
* Edit Local Code
* Test Local Code
* Send to Web Server
* Test Web Pages
* Commit All Changes

### Create a simple plan
* Bullet list of features
* Break down into 20 minute tasks
* To Do List --> Done List


